Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是  这是从厨房拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  只是食材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,利用墨鱼干、泡菜、油炸沙丁鱼、乌鱼子、开心果…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全是世界珍味啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打算将这做成…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由我独创的面向世界的拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉面？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  命名「世界珍味面」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺利完成了我再请你们品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯  我会期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暗影都已经行动了你可真悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时  最重要的就是保持平常心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  说起来的确如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  碎片的妖精操纵了A班的学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千雨似乎也被操纵过了吧  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也对呢  不过完全不记得被操纵时所发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢  我就突然在想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是按照怎样的基准来决定人选的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基准？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被妖精操纵的人之间或许有什么共同点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯嗯  说不定这将成为揭开碎片谜底的提示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,共同点么  比如？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许所有人都和千雨一样身为网络偶像之类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说我才不是网络偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「网络偶像」应该不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那么是被选上的人体重相同！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鹤同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  夏美当时也被操纵了  我来问问她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…「体重」也不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  不会是「体重」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈  是呢  讨厌  我真像个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有短讯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是千鹤姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.32,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}像个傻瓜。\N啊哈哈。\N　　　　　千鹤\N---END---
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇…不留情面呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  美空  这个姿势…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美空  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美空…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失去资格？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错！失去资格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不配做佐佐木莳绘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这出戏也没必要演得这么勉强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不演得彻底怎么能心情舒畅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不配做佐佐木莳绘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  涅吉老师  要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  班长同学  没什么  只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说伊文洁琳因头痛卧床不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊文同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啊  卡莫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是和隆道约好此事不张扬的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长大姐  忘记我刚才说的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉去探病吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  事情闹大了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,万分惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:06:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们去那边的花圃里采些花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用叫上其他同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…还是不要太多人一哄而上…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,设想真是周到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不配做佐佐木莳绘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好  刚想去找您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（伊文小屋）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  茶茶丸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊文同学病情加重了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  主人精神百倍…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是「睡得香、长得快」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀  的确成长迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成长得离谱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不祥的预感…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玉屋～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是暗影  一定是受到暗影的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  不知道她想去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:41.74,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（女生宿舍）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再等一会儿哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（休息室）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非做不可吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好害羞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了  准备OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃跑吗  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使逃跑她也一定会追来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,热情高涨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  要上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀～救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈～哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绿色的茶和其它什么的乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以下省略！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一塌糊涂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在下正是黑蔷薇男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快！拍手～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～谢谢谢谢  哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蔷薇～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家！不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  事件发生了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊  涅加涅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蔷薇～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蔷薇～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候多了一位男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～涅吉弟弟  不是啦不是  她是冒牌货啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冒牌货？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  木乃香啊  怎么可以取下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别叫我冒牌货！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,彻头彻尾的冒牌货啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么明日菜同学会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是借来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,借来？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是赠送了卓柏T恤后借来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卓柏T恤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来涅加涅小姐从早上开始就穿着它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说涅吉小弟  不是出大事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！对！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错！紧急状况！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急状况？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忍！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是伊文…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好大～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家请赶快逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧！现在就由我这个黑蔷薇男爵来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学  别玩了  快逃吧  真的很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪有在胡闹  我是认真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蔷薇～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蔷薇～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是瞎搅和的时候吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快  快！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅加涅小姐  说这话有没有根据啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她是伊文啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:21.06,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（因为她是伊文洁琳  所以没事）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.77,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（十分危险）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全员退避——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦咦咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是正确的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学也赶快…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以丢下你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊文同学  是我  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊文同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快…快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很重啊  快！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,万一受伤了可怎么办啊  笨涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对对对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想想办法可不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,茶茶丸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不如找高畑老师商量商量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:11:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隆道  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高畑老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…其实呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用刚才那些世界珍味做成了拉面？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  似乎失败了呢  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,面向世界还很遥远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隆道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本能？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  恐怕伊文并非意志驱使…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是根据想去上学的本能而行动着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊文洁琳喜欢上学的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  说她讨厌上学也不为过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说喜欢  不如说是体内根深蒂固的习惯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主人总共不由分说地上了15年中学…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,15年…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真漫长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大化的伊文洁琳·A·K·麦克杜威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,服从长年累月的本能来到了学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像往常般地在屋顶睡起了午觉～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎睡得很香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别去管她说不定就会恢复从前了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有干什么坏事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在睡觉而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉小弟  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校舍…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法承受伊文同学的体重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学校毁了不也很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…学校的存亡暂且不去管…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  这样也行吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是那样  这里岂不是也不安全了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…的确
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校舍塌了这边也会受影响
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会一起坍塌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！？  这里可不能坍塌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家来赶快集合！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（为巨大化的伊文同学出谋划策会议）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事态严重  请大家一起出谋划策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  朝仓同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用魔法解决吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的魔法还不够强大…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高畑老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃坏肚子后卧床不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？不会吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了「世界珍味面」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「世界珍味面」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  这是什么面？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没听说过那种面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那涅加涅小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…姐姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偷吃「世界珍味面」后倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「世界珍味面」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  只有靠我们想办法为伊文同学做些什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说「世界珍味面」是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:14:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:14:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请说  真名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,强制驱赶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请再考虑一下稳妥的方法吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有本事你刺激她试试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等她大闹一番将学校瞬间移为平地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「世界珍味面」是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  不如去说服她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「求你了  给我死下来！」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎不太会听我们劝解…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  刚才那是命令  哪是说服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做些能吸引她注意的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那一般是指天邪鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说天岩户
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次表现平平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,30分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,15分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  刚才我说的是正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用做得那么麻烦  直接用绳索从上空吊走不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从上空？要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用什么东西一鼓作气地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总会有办法嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏美  轮到你出场咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一生都不会忘记你的这份勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  夏美…  永别了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不去  我绝对不会去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请  夕映同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和香似乎有话想说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是  和香同学想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定我的百科词典里会有答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搭档  宫崎和香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向我展现出来吧  那隐藏着的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,契约
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发动！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  是成功卡喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  只要使用和香同学的百科词典…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…问题就能迎刃而解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了  和香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能对巨大化的伊文洁琳采取的措施
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样定义是否过于含糊了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  真的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「就让她静静地安睡吧」…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世间可没想象中那么单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,博士  千雨同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我早料到会有此事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.11,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（机械卡布拉2号  校舍前）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,获得千羽千羽的协力后强化了的机械卡布拉2号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别叫我千羽千羽！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么又是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里强化了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顶部着色了
