Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样协助的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓了  总之就拜托了  叶加濑大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…叶加濑同学…打算用机械卡布拉做些什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～又冒烟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失败了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想找机会反问我们「失败了吗…」而已吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呜…涅吉老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  总算还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到达极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,崩塌进入倒计读秒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伴奏笛声…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,茶茶丸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢快的旋律喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊文…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被笛声吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学校得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着笛声走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像哈莫尔恩的笛声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  隆道
