Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太感动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  在千钧一发之际避免了学校的崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法世界确确实实在产生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:20:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风雨即将来临…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睁大你的眼睛期待下集吧！
